Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.91,0:01:22.47,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}{\blur5}君を待った
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.47,0:01:24.01,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}{\blur5}僕は待った
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.01,0:01:27.12,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}{\blur5}途切れない明日も過ぎて行って
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.12,0:01:28.66,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}{\blur5}立ち止まって
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.66,0:01:30.21,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}{\blur5}振り返って
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.21,0:01:33.25,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}{\blur5}とめどない今日を嘆き合った
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.25,0:01:34.86,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}{\blur5}記憶だって
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.86,0:01:36.38,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}{\blur5}永遠になんて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.38,0:01:39.48,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}{\blur5}残らないものとおもい知って
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.48,0:01:42.60,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}{\blur5}僕はずっと　掻きむしって
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.60,0:01:44.78,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}{\blur5}心の隅っこで泣いて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.78,0:01:46.68,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}{\blur5}そしてどうか
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.68,0:01:48.48,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}{\blur5}なくさないでよって
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.48,0:01:51.64,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}{\blur5}高架下、過ぎる日々を
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.64,0:01:58.11,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}{\blur5}後悔してんだよって　そう言い逃したあの日
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.11,0:01:59.57,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}{\blur5}君を待った
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.57,0:02:01.09,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}{\blur5}僕は待った
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.09,0:02:04.29,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}{\blur5}途切れない明日も過ぎて行って
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.29,0:02:07.35,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}{\blur5}僕は今日も掻きむしって
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.35,0:02:11.54,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}{\blur5}忘れない傷をつけてるんだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.13,0:02:18.57,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}{\blur5}君じゃないとさ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.91,0:01:22.47,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}{\blur4}等待著你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.47,0:01:24.01,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}{\blur4}我在等著
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.01,0:01:27.12,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}{\blur4}不會中斷的明天也過去了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.12,0:01:28.66,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}{\blur4}停下腳步
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.66,0:01:30.21,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}{\blur4}回頭望去
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.21,0:01:33.25,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}{\blur4}悲歎著無止境的今天
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.25,0:01:34.86,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}{\blur4}記憶也是
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.86,0:01:36.38,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}{\blur4}永遠什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.38,0:01:39.48,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}{\blur4}讓我認識到那不會留下
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.48,0:01:42.60,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}{\blur4}我一直在抓狂
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.60,0:01:44.78,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}{\blur4}在心靈的角落中哭泣著
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.78,0:01:46.68,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}{\blur4}然而請務必
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.68,0:01:48.48,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}{\blur4}不要丟掉
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.48,0:01:51.64,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}{\blur4}那高架橋下度過的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.64,0:01:58.11,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}{\blur4}喊著「我在後悔」卻走掉的那一天
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.11,0:01:59.57,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}{\blur4}等待著你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.57,0:02:01.09,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}{\blur4}我在等著
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.09,0:02:04.29,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}{\blur4}不會中斷的明天已經過去了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.29,0:02:07.35,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}{\blur4}我今天依然在抓狂
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.35,0:02:11.54,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}{\blur4}為自己添加著無法忘記的傷口
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.13,0:02:18.57,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}{\blur4}沒有你一起的話
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.48,0:21:31.26,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,0)}{\blur4}僕だけが見てた君のこと
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.26,0:21:44.59,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}過去も未来も　かなしみもよろこびも全て
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.59,0:21:54.99,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}オトナになるってきっと優しくなることだと信じていた
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.99,0:22:00.84,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}子供の頃の僕のままに
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.84,0:22:05.23,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}君のこと守りたいと思う
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.23,0:22:07.92,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}暗闇から目覚めても
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.92,0:22:12.70,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}僕を待ち受けてる彼方で
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.70,0:22:22.85,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}二人を隠したこの街に誰も知らない雪が降っていた
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.85,0:22:32.07,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}君が僕の胸に刻まれた一番深い傷跡のようで
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.07,0:22:47.45,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}{\fad(0,4000)}君が笑うこの世界の歌　取り戻すよ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.48,0:21:31.26,EDCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,0)}{\blur6}只有我看到了你的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.26,0:21:44.59,EDCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}過去 未來 悲傷 快樂 一切的一切
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.59,0:21:54.99,EDCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur6}一直相信著成為大人後一定能變得溫柔
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.99,0:22:00.84,EDCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur6}在我現在還小的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.84,0:22:05.23,EDCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur6}就決定要保護你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.23,0:22:07.92,EDCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur6}即便在黑暗中醒來
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.92,0:22:12.70,EDCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur6}在等待著我的彼方
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.70,0:22:22.85,EDCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur6}藏匿著兩人的這個城市下著無人所知的雪
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.85,0:22:32.07,EDCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur6}就像你在我心裡刻下了最深刻的傷痕一般
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.07,0:22:47.45,EDCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur6}{\fad(0,4000)}你所歡笑著的這個世界的歌 我一定會取回來
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.36,0:00:14.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是悟嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.91,0:00:18.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.97,0:00:23.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.18,0:02:44.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.01,0:02:46.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.68,0:02:49.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼早做什麼呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.26,0:02:52.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做什麼？一看就知道吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.19,0:02:55.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你今天也要早點去上學吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.36,0:02:59.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我開動了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.51,0:03:04.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用那麼著急吃啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.90,0:03:08.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悟 我能單刀直入地問嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.45,0:03:09.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.93,0:03:12.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個點你要和誰去做什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.05,0:03:15.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保密
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.08,0:03:19.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是在做壞事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.45,0:03:21.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.97,0:03:24.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就行
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.11,0:03:27.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我走…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.69,0:03:28.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.89,0:03:30.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把這個帶去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.47,0:03:34.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼早就出門的話 沒到中午就餓了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.34,0:03:38.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.34,0:03:55.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雛月 早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.96,0:03:59.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好 悟
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.72,0:04:01.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給 早餐
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.60,0:04:03.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個不是悟的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.98,0:04:05.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經吃過了 沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.93,0:04:10.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺好棒
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.76,0:04:12.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉啊 加代
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.07,0:04:13.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡很無聊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.64,0:04:15.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少有臺電視也好啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.28,0:04:21.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事 昨天廣美君拿了許多書給我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.67,0:04:25.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想一定只需要再忍一兩天就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.70,0:04:31.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.15,0:04:34.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那放學後再見
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.26,0:04:50.68,OTHER_03,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz8.423\pos(578,188)}{\b1}我都放了些兒子喜歡吃的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.69,0:04:55.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.60,0:04:58.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,泉水小的小孩們都漸漸來上學了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.12,0:05:01.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是呆得久了點
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.07,0:05:07.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,畢業典禮的致辭好不想做啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.79,0:05:09.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.18,0:05:12.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明是彩更擅長朗讀啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.09,0:05:13.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.47,0:05:15.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早季能行的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.70,0:05:19.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鼓起勇氣做吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.16,0:05:27.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加代今天也缺席吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.09,0:05:29.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藤沼 你沒聽說什麼嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.54,0:05:32.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 早上去她那也沒人理我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.57,0:05:35.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是感冒了嗎 雛月那傢伙怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.76,0:05:39.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學校都沒有收到聯絡的確很奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.69,0:05:42.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an3}一般來說她媽會聯絡學校吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.69,0:05:43.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9}雛月沒事吧 好擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.11,0:05:44.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1}雛月經常休息啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.21,0:05:44.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an3}我也想休息
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.13,0:05:50.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然是加代的話 說不定突然就會回來上學的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.17,0:05:51.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開始上課吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.82,0:05:56.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.21,0:05:58.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天你也到她家去了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.80,0:06:00.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很擔心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.68,0:06:03.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過你倒是挺冷靜的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.96,0:06:05.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師不也經常說嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.95,0:06:09.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,越是這種情況就越應該和平時一樣冷靜
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.52,0:06:10.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.79,0:06:15.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在昨天和今天都打了電話給加代家 都沒人接
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.46,0:06:19.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也打了電話給她母親的單位 說是缺勤
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.23,0:06:23.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師！能聯繫員警或者兒童諮詢所嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.63,0:06:26.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,員警嗎… 這個嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.55,0:06:30.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在報警的話 會不會有人會覺得困擾？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.14,0:06:36.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天我聯繫了兒諮
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.33,0:06:38.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說是今天會來
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.39,0:06:40.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也會跟著一起到加代那去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.97,0:06:44.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概問題的根源就在那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.15,0:06:47.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,畢竟是我說的任何事都要盡全力啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.58,0:06:50.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝老師
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.59,0:06:55.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,八代原來有動作嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.51,0:06:57.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.29,0:07:03.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雛月女士 我們是石狩振興局的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.98,0:07:07.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.44,0:07:10.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,燈是開著的 裡面應該有人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.00,0:07:13.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,繞到後面去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.96,0:07:17.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雛月女士 在家嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.32,0:07:19.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加代
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.15,0:07:24.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打擾了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.55,0:07:25.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.85,0:07:29.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係 責任由我來負
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.17,0:07:32.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,據說都失蹤了三天
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.50,0:07:34.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就交給他吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.47,0:07:47.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,電器和暖爐都開著
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.28,0:07:49.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,近期的進食痕跡是一人份
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.30,0:07:52.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有加代的上衣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.58,0:07:57.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她母親至少剛才還在這
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.68,0:08:02.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該是在我們抵達的同時 她母親從陽臺逃掉了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.12,0:08:03.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是頭疼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.61,0:08:06.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還想著起碼能保護到女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.49,0:08:08.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天早上再過來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.41,0:08:11.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想她母親應該是穿著室內便服出去的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.33,0:08:13.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們離開的話應該就會回來
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.67,0:08:16.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女孩不知道有沒有事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.20,0:08:19.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有讓員警尋找她母親的手段
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.64,0:08:22.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 加代應該沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.68,0:08:25.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我稍微有點頭緒
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.18,0:08:27.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然老師都這麼說了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.19,0:08:30.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼我們暫時撤退 等她母親冷靜下來再說吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.97,0:08:34.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兒童諮詢所的人來了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.45,0:08:36.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,八代老師也是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.02,0:08:39.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雛月的媽媽不在家
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.30,0:08:42.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概在今天或者明天就能做了斷
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.42,0:08:43.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加代
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.71,0:08:46.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要跟你媽分開了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.11,0:08:49.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是非常令人開心的事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.01,0:08:55.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雛月加代被保護的同時也代表著要與我們分開
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.76,0:08:58.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.53,0:09:02.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一想到大家 心情就會變得溫暖
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.62,0:09:06.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悟 雖然遲了點…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.58,0:09:10.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是生日禮物
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.86,0:09:12.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.73,0:09:17.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,禮物明天就給你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.32,0:09:18.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,約好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.37,0:09:31.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.92,0:09:35.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺這一瞬間…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.94,0:09:39.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直在等待著
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.20,0:09:45.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悟 你的淚腺出奇的松嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.06,0:09:51.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 悟 今晚就住這吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.84,0:09:53.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好大膽！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.35,0:09:58.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的 雖然沒有出什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.41,0:10:02.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是昨天晚上 有人來過這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.82,0:10:04.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.97,0:10:08.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保安 值宿員 校務員
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.31,0:10:09.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有其他的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.23,0:10:13.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰把黃書藏這了之類的？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.79,0:10:15.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是個大人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.58,0:10:19.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還踢了一腳紙箱 好像是生氣了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.17,0:10:21.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打開看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.53,0:10:24.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是黃書就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.87,0:10:39.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.08,0:10:42.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些究竟是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.43,0:10:45.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有我一瞬間就理解了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.04,0:10:52.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後我終於想起這個泉水小是連續誘拐殺人事件第二個犧牲者
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.25,0:10:56.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中西彩就讀的學校
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.06,0:11:03.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們還處於事件的迴圈中
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.01,0:11:11.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,3月2日
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.84,0:11:14.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,22點到23點之間
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.32,0:11:17.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雛月加代從自家的庫房中失蹤
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.04,0:11:21.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,庫房周圍留下的橡膠長靴的腳印
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.69,0:11:23.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,與白鳥家所持有的一致
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.17,0:11:28.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在業務用冷凍庫內使用噴霧器
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.87,0:11:30.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,使其迅速凍死
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.50,0:11:36.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後在日出之前將凍死的屍體放回庫房
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.47,0:11:42.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個巴士不行
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.91,0:11:47.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡處於事件迴圈的正中央
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.77,0:11:52.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趕緊離開這裡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.70,0:11:55.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.35,0:11:57.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然很希望雛被人發現
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.80,0:12:00.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但感覺很危險啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.60,0:12:02.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡面的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.28,0:12:05.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是變態就不好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.75,0:12:09.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悟 你有其他計畫嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.96,0:12:11.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.26,0:12:14.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,OK 那我們撤退吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.59,0:12:23.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,記著 這是那傢伙的腳印
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.33,0:12:28.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼東西 這些黑色的粉末
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.24,0:12:32.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是煤球
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.96,0:12:36.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莫非這也是真犯的…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.95,0:12:45.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡！ 可惡！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.36,0:12:48.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悟 那些東西都不用管了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.82,0:12:51.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.26,0:12:54.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 我慌起來有什麼用
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.61,0:12:58.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 就這樣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.43,0:13:00.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明是個好藏身處啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.57,0:13:03.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚上會有人來的藏身處是不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.63,0:13:10.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在就算來點硬的也要盡可能讓雛月遠離事件的迴圈
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.69,0:13:12.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兒諮也開始行動了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.74,0:13:16.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們的行動確確實實地改變著未來
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.78,0:13:19.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定會順利的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.51,0:13:24.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悟…這就是下一個計畫？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.11,0:13:28.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很直接吧 再深入一步吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.33,0:13:31.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事到如今居然正面上啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.00,0:13:32.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.25,0:13:34.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎回來
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.83,0:13:40.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚 晚上好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.92,0:13:45.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悟 說明一下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.18,0:13:53.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為沒有半路拋棄就變成這樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.13,0:14:05.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們幹得好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.12,0:14:08.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就知道你會這麼說
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.54,0:14:11.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然也想過會先被教訓一頓
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.53,0:14:13.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.20,0:14:15.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有什麼該教訓的地方吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.27,0:14:17.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是為了朋友才做的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.10,0:14:23.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我從剛才就一直很在意了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.41,0:14:24.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個味道是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.63,0:14:27.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為感覺你也差不多該回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.54,0:14:30.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過不知道會來幾個人 就做了咖喱
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.89,0:14:33.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然都露餡了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.56,0:14:37.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們也別傻站著 進來吃咖喱吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.68,0:14:38.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打擾了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.56,0:14:40.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不客氣了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.63,0:14:44.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是沒人來的話怎麼辦啊 這個量
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.06,0:14:48.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正咖喱能吃好幾天
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.65,0:14:52.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…這個
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.28,0:14:54.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.88,0:14:56.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,承蒙款待
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.69,0:15:02.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那剩下的就交給我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.71,0:15:05.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說的可不是收拾哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.01,0:15:06.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.65,0:15:07.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.25,0:15:08.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.40,0:15:09.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.12,0:15:13.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.26,0:15:15.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是藤沼悟的母親
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.07,0:15:21.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,八代老師 悟和加代回到我家來了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.33,0:15:23.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎 那太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.17,0:15:26.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就知道會這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.25,0:15:32.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然事情會演變成加代被哪裡的設施所收容嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.17,0:15:34.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.13,0:15:38.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這方面我有些想法
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.96,0:15:42.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 沒能見到加代的母親
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.96,0:15:46.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有 藤沼女士 我有一個請求
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.14,0:15:48.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.90,0:15:50.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼就在明早七點
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.08,0:15:55.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加代 今天就住下來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.35,0:16:01.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初次見面
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.91,0:16:03.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大晚上的真是抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.51,0:16:06.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是美琴小的教師八代學
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.10,0:16:09.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想和您討論一下加代的事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.15,0:16:12.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個叫做奇跡小子 很帥氣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.20,0:16:17.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們倆誰先洗澡？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.00,0:16:19.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你先去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.27,0:16:21.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.93,0:16:24.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你和我一起洗吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.59,0:16:34.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加代 我來幫你洗頭吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.95,0:16:36.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我自己會洗…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.65,0:16:38.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啦好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.79,0:16:44.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,客官 請問哪裡覺得癢的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.01,0:16:47.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.65,0:16:49.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.01,0:16:54.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.21,0:16:57.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是說這裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.45,0:17:00.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.26,0:17:03.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我振作點啊 29歲！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.79,0:17:09.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好好擦乾的話會感冒的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.93,0:17:19.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感 感覺你挺開心的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.60,0:17:22.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很溫暖
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.48,0:17:24.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.83,0:17:27.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那件睡衣…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.10,0:17:29.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我買的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.55,0:17:31.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這妖孽…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.86,0:17:34.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,床單我洗過了 把這個拿去用吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.73,0:17:36.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.59,0:17:38.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悟 太亂了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.30,0:17:40.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那邊再拉過去一點
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.71,0:17:42.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺像修學旅行一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.72,0:17:47.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來 函館山上看到的夜景真的好棒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.28,0:17:49.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一次都沒去過函館吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.99,0:17:50.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.89,0:17:54.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 我只是在照片上看過
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.95,0:17:57.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 要關燈了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.45,0:17:58.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.36,0:18:02.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.67,0:18:04.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為平時都是關著的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.82,0:18:07.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎 那我關掉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.61,0:18:10.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 開著就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.05,0:18:11.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就這樣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.71,0:18:14.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.20,0:18:15.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.21,0:18:18.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.33,0:18:20.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.03,0:18:34.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是不是很礙事？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.81,0:18:37.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒 沒這種事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.32,0:18:39.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰會嗯的！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.70,0:18:39.22,Default02,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.58,0:18:41.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你幹什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.84,0:18:43.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,囉嗦！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.58,0:18:44.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.22,0:18:45.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快住手啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.30,0:18:46.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.06,0:18:48.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你傻嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.96,0:19:08.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.71,0:19:10.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.19,0:19:11.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.85,0:19:16.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悟 加代 趁熱吃了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.02,0:19:17.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.45,0:19:27.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我開動了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.82,0:19:29.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咖喱呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.96,0:19:32.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暫時會是悟的晚飯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.25,0:19:35.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是還有五六人的份嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.42,0:19:38.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再把大家叫來不就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.84,0:21:02.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.53,0:21:09.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加代！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.54,0:21:11.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好幾天的 你死哪去了！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.88,0:21:13.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個…！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.52,0:21:16.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們…


